@Audit.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5171

### Liveness probe
GET {{Audit.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Audit a real URL (my choice)
POST {{Audit.Api_HostAddress}}/api/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.python.org"
}

### Validation: rejects a non-absolute URL (expect 400 problem details)
POST {{Audit.Api_HostAddress}}/api/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "not-a-url"
}
